<h2>Autodesk</h2>
<p>
  Computer-aided design software provided another solution when generating 3D models. In particular, I experimented with the 
  design software <a href="https://www.autodesk.com/products/fusion-360/overview?term=1-YEAR&support=null">Autodesk: Fusion 360</a>
  to generate 3D models that scaled according to the wall space in my apartment's living room. Autodesk provided an intuitive platform 
  with which to build and export 3D models that matched my apartment floorplan.
</p>
<center>
  <%= image_tag "Autodesk.png", :class => "style_image", :size => "450x300" %>
</center>
